                "section": "Lion's mane mushroom marination (2 hours prior)",
                "steps": [
                    "Prep the marinade in a large tray at least 2 hours prior to assembling the sandwich",
                    "Gentry fry the mushrooms in oil on each side for 5 minutes, then gentry press down.",
                    "Flip, and ensure the mushrooms are cooked until golden brown on both sides.",
                    "Plane mushrooms in marinade and marinate for 30 minutes to 2 hours."
