                ]
            },
            {
                "section": "Assembly",
                "steps": [
                    "Prep pickled onions, slice chiabatta (and toast) in half lengthwise and assemble the mayo sauce.",
                    "Take the mushrooms out of the marinade and fly in oil on a medium to high heat until charred.",
                    "Slice mushrooms into 1-2cm pieces.",
                    "To assemble, slather each side of the chiabatta in the mayo sauce, place on sliced mushrooms, pickled onions and rocket."
